descriptionHtml: Miss NayOhm is a follower I had built with creation kit. She is a mix of all the actors i thought best in the game. Lydia,  Annekke,  Brelyna Maryon,  J'zargo,  Mirabelle Ervine and as a fraction follower, "Dragon" . She is carrying each 5000, as the file will download 2 followers. one, NayOhm "Demon"  will not follow and 2 named Miss NayOhm, Nord that do and are eligible for marriage. They top at level 80, and start at level 15 , avoids death never dies. Can be found just outside of Honningbrew Meadery.  If Calientes is installed Miss NayOhm might be nude though I clothed her in Dragon priest outfit. Very helpfull, 70 % of the game has been tested with her and has never failed me. More pics can be seen with Steam, profiles http;//steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561198120548710/screenshots. Thanks and big smiles. Oh , and remember they are nude.
